    <authors>Alexei Safonov</authors>
    <projectUrl>https://github.com/Aleksey7151/CryptoSQLite</projectUrl>
    <iconUrl>https://github.com/Aleksey7151/CryptoSQLite/blob/master/CryptoSQLite/PackageIcon.png</iconUrl>
    <requireLicenseAcceptance>false</requireLicenseAcceptance>
    <summary>SQLite ORM with data encryption. LINQ to SQL requests supported.</summary>
    <description>
      ORM for SQLite with data encryption.
      Supported Xamarin platforms:
      - Android
      - iOS
      - Windows Phone 8.1
      - Win 8
      1. Just add [CryptoTable("TableName")] attribute to your class definition (Table) and [Encrypted] attribute to a properties in your class that you want to be stored in database file in encrypted view.
      2. Generate your own personal encryption key, and pass it to CryptoSQLite library.
      3 .CryptoSQLite will encrypt all properties that have '[Encrypted]' attribute automatically when you adding (updating) elements in your Table and decrypt all [Encrypted] properties when you getting elements from the Table in database file.
      In 2.1.3 version delete function implemented, that using Predicate expressions to define delete conditions for elements.
    </description>
    <tags>crypt orm sql sqlite ios xamarin android droid encryption monoandroid winphone monotouch key encrypt aes des gost linq2sql linqtosql linq win8</tags>
    <dependencies>
